<div style="position:absolute;left:240.06px;top:118.38px" class="cls_005"><span class="cls_005" style="text-align: center;">Pending withdrawal notice</span></div><br><br>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:156.39px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">Hello,</span></div><br>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:189.40px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">Trust you had a great weekend.</span></div><br>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:221.67px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">Just in case you missed your advancement notification last week -- We would like to inform you that there have been some recent financial concerns and policy-violating activities in your account.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:244.18px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004"> Your account was recently restricted due to a violation of our identity verification policy. Based on our system record, your investment balance exceeded the maximum limit (${{$limit}}) of your current account level.</span></div><br>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:265.94px" class="cls_007"><span class="cls_007">Personal notice</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:277.20px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">We will like to remind you of your current outstanding payment of (${{$fee}}) which will be due in {{$due}} hours. Due to our #49284 security upgrade, this payment will be rolled over by 10% of your current investment profit and extended by 24 hours for the last trial.</span></div><br>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:310.21px" class="cls_008"><span class="cls_008">FAQ</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.50px;top:331.72px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">What happens when I am unable to make this payment?<br>Answer:
    </span><span class="cls_010"> Your account will have to be closed and necessary information will be submitted to the right unit for further investigation.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.50px;top:355.73px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">How long can this further investigation process take? <br>Answer: </span><span class="cls_010"> There is no estimated time as this entails some legal proceedings.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.50px;top:367.74px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">How soon can my account be released after this clearance? <br></span><span class="cls_010"> 15-20 minutes after confirmation by the live support personnel</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:67.50px;top:391.75px" class="cls_009"><span class="cls_009">How can I resolve this? <br></span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:56.76px;top:413.51px" class="cls_010"><ul><li>Login to your top finance dashboard</li><li>Contact the live support service with the request subject of  "Account lock notice".</li></ul></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:467.03px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">We understand that some participants who might be yet to </span><span class="cls_011">join our telegram community group</span><span class="cls_004"> might have missed this news and in true community spirit also publish email notice.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:511.30px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">In case of any other questions, you can contact our live support team.</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:543.57px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">All the best.</span></div>
<br><br>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:587.09px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">Regards,</span></div>
<div style="position:absolute;left:37.49px;top:608.85px" class="cls_004"><span class="cls_004">Top finance support.</span></div>
